      `‚ùå Domain tanpa Data: ${noDataDomains.length}\n` +
      `üìà Persentase Ketersediaan: ${calculatePercentage(totalSuccessfulAnalytics, domainCount)}%\n\n` +
      (noDataDomains.length > 0 ? 
